---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import img from "../assets/jen.jpg";
---

<Layout
  title="About Beanpot Studio | Our Mission and Founder"
  description="Meet Jen Looper and the Beanpot Studio team—building practical, AI-aware software for real life."
>
  <section
    class="scroll-mt-[4.5rem] border-t border-primary-200/50 bg-primary-50/90"
    aria-labelledby="about-title"
  >
    <div class="section-padding container-custom">
      <header class="mb-10 flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-3 sm:mb-12">
        <p class="kicker">Our story</p>
        <h1
          id="about-title"
          class="font-display text-display-1 font-semibold text-primary-950"
        >
          About
        </h1>
        <p
          class="max-w-prose font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-primary-800 sm:text-lg"
        >
          A small Boston studio—product-minded, family-oriented, and focused on
          tools people actually use.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12"
      >
        <div class="min-w-0 lg:col-span-7">
          <div
            class="rounded-2xl border border-primary-200/40 bg-white/90 p-8 ring-1 ring-primary-200/20 shadow-craft sm:p-10"
          >
            <p
              class="max-w-prose font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-primary-800 sm:text-lg"
            >
              Welcome! I&apos;m Jen Looper, founder and CEO of Beanpot
              Studio—where great things are cooking, built in Boston. I have
              more than 25 years&apos; experience as a web and mobile developer,
              building creative cross-platform products that solve
              <em>real</em> problems: how families build practice habits, how small
              teams ship reliable software, and how AI can support people in real
              life.
            </p>
            <p
              class="mt-6 max-w-prose font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-primary-800 sm:text-lg"
            >
              I&apos;m the Director of Developer Relations at Cloudinary, and
              I&apos;ve served as Head of Academic Advocacy at AWS, Principal
              Cloud Developer Advocate at Microsoft, and Developer Advocate at
              Progress/Telerik. I design curricula on technical topics, have
              founded a nonprofit, and have worked at organizations of every
              size. That mix shapes how we approach product at Beanpot: clear
              communication, high craft, and empathy for the user.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm lg:col-span-5 lg:max-w-none lg:justify-self-end"
        >
          <figure
            class="w-full max-w-sm motion-reduce:rotate-0 lg:max-w-md -rotate-1"
          >
            <Image
              src={img}
              alt="Portrait of Jen Looper, founder of Beanpot Studio"
              class="h-auto w-full rounded-2xl border border-primary-200/30 shadow-craft"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
